=== nega_reward_dice ===
~ intro = nega_reward_dice == 1

- (give_reward)

/character nega hand_out
Hand it over.

- (give_reward_fail)

+ [pose:present_wrist_reward] -> HoldPose(-> give_reward_fail, -> give_reward) ->
+ [no] -> Nega_CheckIfInterested -> give_reward

- /perform swipe_hand
~ rewards--

/perform chuckle
Fuck ya!
You're my bitch now.

/perform give_dice

+ [hold:dice]
        Let's see what you're going to get
    for this pretty little gift.
    
- (roll) 
/perform lean_forward_from_squat
Go ahead. Roll them bones.

+ [roll]
+ [timeout] -> roll

- ~ temp result1 = getNegaDie1()
~ temp result2 = getNegaDie2()
~ temp result3 = getNegaDie3()
~ temp result = result1 + result2 + result3

Results: <>
~ rollToText(result1)
<> + <>
~ rollToText(result2)
<> + <>
~ rollToText(result3)

{
    - intro && result > 0: -> intro_reward
    - intro: -> intro_change_dice
    
    - result == 3: -> result_reward_hard
    - result == 2: -> result_reward_light
    - result == 1: -> result_reward_tease
    
    - result1 == 0 && result2 == 0 && result3 == 0: -> result_all_blank
    - result == 0: -> result_no_reward

    - result == -1: -> result_punishment_tease
    - result == -2: -> result_punishment_light
    - result == -3: -> result_punishment_hard
}


- (result_reward_hard)
/perform behold
Oooo, three cups! You are a lucky little shit.
That does <i>not</i> happen often.

/perform cock_head_to_left
I suppose I have to give you something very special, then, don't I?

