- (result_reward_tease)

// This can either be 2 cups and a skull or 1 cup and two blanks.

{ result1 == -1 || result2 == -1 || result3 == -1:
    /perform curious
    Two cups and a skull, hmm?
    /perform open_arms_shrug
    Skulls cancel cups, I'm afraid, so that's one cup for you.
- else:
    /perform curious
    Hmm.. one cup.
}

/perform open_arms_shrug
Not bad. But not great.
I suppose you deserve a little something for that.

