- (result_all_blank)

/perform serious
Wow, that is by far the best bad luck I've ever seen.
You get nothing, of course, but for a roll like that...

/perform lean_forward
{ negaLoreEmpty():
    perhaps I'll make an exception.
    -> result_punishment_tease_no_intro
- else:
    perhaps I'll let you in on a little secret.
    -> nega_lore
}

- (result_no_reward)

TODO: Write 'no reward' dialog here.

/perform cocks_head_to_left
Well look at that. Skull and cup cancel each other out.
Nothing for you today. Better luck next time, bitch.
/perform laughs

-> exit


- (result_punishment_tease)

{ result1 == 1 || result2 == 1 || result3 == 1:
    /perform fake_annoyed
    Two skulls and a cup, hmm?
    Cups cancel skulls, alas, so only one little skull for you.
- else:
    /perform thoughtful
    Hmm.. one skull.
}

/perform curious
I suppose I can't go too hard on you,
/perform lean_forward
but I bet I can still make you squirm.

